---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import { Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import headshot from "../images/headshot.jpg";
import ogImageURL from "../../utils/ogImageURL";
---

<Layout
	tags={{
		title: "About | Chris LaRocque",
		description:
			"Chris LaRocque is a web developer from Boston, MA. He specializes in tactical agile development aimed at delivering user-centric software at scale and at speed.",
		imageURL: ogImageURL({
			title: "About",
			subtitle: "About me, Chris LaRocque, and how to get in touch.",
		}),
	}}
>
	<main>
		<section class="justify-center gap-7 lg:flex">
			<div class="text-wrapper content flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="text py-7">
					<h1 class="">About me</h1>
					<div
						class="my-7 flex max-w-[50%] justify-between lg:max-w-[12%]"
					>
						<a href="https://twitter.com/TophLaRoph">
							<svg
								width="24"
								height="24"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								fill="currentColor"
								class="scale-150"
								><path
									d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm6.066 9.645c.183 4.04-2.83 8.544-8.164 8.544-1.622 0-3.131-.476-4.402-1.291 1.524.18 3.045-.244 4.252-1.189-1.256-.023-2.317-.854-2.684-1.995.451.086.895.061 1.298-.049-1.381-.278-2.335-1.522-2.304-2.853.388.215.83.344 1.301.359-1.279-.855-1.641-2.544-.889-3.835 1.416 1.738 3.533 2.881 5.92 3.001-.419-1.796.944-3.527 2.799-3.527.825 0 1.572.349 2.096.907.654-.128 1.27-.368 1.824-.697-.215.671-.67 1.233-1.263 1.589.581-.07 1.135-.224 1.649-.453-.384.578-.87 1.084-1.433 1.489z"
								></path></svg
							>
						</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/ChrisLaRocque">
							<svg
								fill="currentColor"
								width="24"
								height="24"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								class="scale-150"
								><path
									d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
								></path></svg
							>
						</a>
					</div>
					<p class="max-w-[70ch]">
						I'm a full-stack web developer building responsive,
						user-first websites. I started working in tech at
						Spartan Race, followed by Brightcove. From there I made
						my way to Gatsby as a Senior Solutions Engineer, and
						then eventually to Netlify via aquisition.
						<br /><br />
						I consider myself fortunate to be able to hear how so many
						different teams solve the problems presented by the modern
						web. I get to do as my fellow Netlifolker <a
							href="https://www.chrishannaby.com/"
							>Chris Hannaby</a
						> says and bring all these best-in-class practices not only
						into my own work but to the customers of Netlify/Gatsby in
						an effort to 'uplevel everyone'.
						<br /><br />
						Outside of slinging the future of web tech I am usually (honestly)
						checking out whats new in web tooling, watching old NFL Films
						docs, and chilling with my partner Becca and our insufferable
						bulldog, Alby.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<Picture
				src={headshot}
				widths={[200, 400, 600]}
				sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"
				alt="Chris LaRocque headshot"
				aspectRatio="1:1"
				class="rounded-full"
				loading={"eager"}
				width={600}
				height={600}
			/>
		</section>
		<!-- <section class="justify-center lg:flex">
			<div>
				<h2
					class="border-b-2 border-white p-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight"
				>
					Get in touch
				</h2>
				<div class="m-4 flex justify-center"></div>
			</div>
		</section> -->
	</main>
</Layout>
